# Dependencies
node_modules/
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Bun lockfile is the canonical text lock; commit it via `bun.lock`.
# The binary lockfile `bun.lockb` (older Bun versions) is not used here.
# bun.lock
bun.lockb

